WEBVTT

00:00:07.725 --> 00:00:11.711
♪I found a faint light
in the fading dusk♪

00:00:11.712 --> 00:00:15.311
♪And met your steady gaze♪

00:00:15.312 --> 00:00:24.132
♪One knowing glance,
and side by side we walk on♪

00:00:24.575 --> 00:00:27.061
♪Longing finds no place to rest♪

00:00:27.062 --> 00:00:29.211
♪Through drifting wind and rain♪

00:00:29.212 --> 00:00:32.699
♪You are the prayer within my hands♪

00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:40.324
♪A single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows♪

00:00:40.325 --> 00:00:42.786
♪We made a promise long ago♪

00:00:42.787 --> 00:00:44.786
♪For all our days to come♪

00:00:44.787 --> 00:00:48.449
♪You are the fate I cannot outrun♪

00:00:48.450 --> 00:00:53.836
♪How much must I let go
to trade for one moment?♪

00:00:53.837 --> 00:00:56.457
♪Holding you close♪

00:00:56.637 --> 00:00:58.874
♪Would that be enough?♪

00:00:58.875 --> 00:00:59.619
=Echoes of Love=

00:00:59.620 --> 00:01:01.499
(Adapted from the signed screenplay
Echoes of Love on Migu Reading)

00:01:01.500 --> 00:01:03.682
=Episode 18=

00:01:18.540 --> 00:01:20.179
Lanterns speak for those we miss.

00:01:20.900 --> 00:01:22.500
Since we cannot go in person,

00:01:23.859 --> 00:01:25.579
let this carry our thoughts to her.

00:01:26.979 --> 00:01:28.299
Thank you.

00:01:34.740 --> 00:01:36.019
Shanguan Yu,

00:01:37.300 --> 00:01:38.700
you were

00:01:39.300 --> 00:01:42.579
the bravest and kindest woman
I have ever known.

00:01:43.537 --> 00:01:44.937
Because of me,

00:01:45.287 --> 00:01:47.932
you went through so much.

00:01:50.812 --> 00:01:51.932
It is my fault.

00:01:52.875 --> 00:01:54.267
It is my fault.

00:02:00.540 --> 00:02:02.060
One day,

00:02:04.180 --> 00:02:06.179
I will avenge you.

00:02:07.139 --> 00:02:09.300
Those who wronged you

00:02:09.737 --> 00:02:11.897
will pay.

00:02:52.900 --> 00:02:55.099
Why is life so hard for women?

00:02:55.659 --> 00:02:57.379
After enduring so much,

00:02:57.779 --> 00:02:59.500
there is still no peace at the end.

00:03:00.750 --> 00:03:02.149
If there is another life,

00:03:03.860 --> 00:03:05.179
may she be

00:03:05.180 --> 00:03:07.482
an ordinary woman who knows happiness.

00:03:09.379 --> 00:03:10.699
That would be enough.

00:03:17.339 --> 00:03:20.180
Zhiyun, sleep.

00:03:20.580 --> 00:03:22.300
When you wake,

00:03:22.379 --> 00:03:24.020
things will change.

00:03:24.779 --> 00:03:26.020
Trust me.

00:03:29.860 --> 00:03:31.180
Let's do it together.

00:03:34.339 --> 00:03:35.460
Get some sleep.

00:03:43.825 --> 00:03:45.295
(Now, as planned,)

00:03:45.412 --> 00:03:47.139
(you bring charges against Gao Deng,)

00:03:47.140 --> 00:03:48.819
(and I move to withdraw the case.)

00:03:49.059 --> 00:03:50.580
(This token of loyalty)

00:03:50.659 --> 00:03:52.500
(should be enough to draw them out.)

00:03:53.059 --> 00:03:56.457
Young Lord, Madam Ruyi
invites you for a private meeting.

00:03:57.499 --> 00:04:00.179
(Once I obtain the key evidence,
the jade ruyi,)

00:04:00.180 --> 00:04:01.979
(I can clear my mother's name,)

00:04:02.260 --> 00:04:03.939
(convict Madam Ruyi,)

00:04:04.180 --> 00:04:06.020
(and bring down the Shengtang Guild.)

00:04:06.180 --> 00:04:07.579
(Song Zhiyun, do not worry.)

00:04:07.580 --> 00:04:10.060
(I am going to finish
what matters most to you.)

00:04:13.900 --> 00:04:15.259
This way.

00:04:25.140 --> 00:04:26.659
Young Lord,

00:04:26.940 --> 00:04:28.859
with your noble lineage,

00:04:29.299 --> 00:04:30.899
and both wit and valor,

00:04:30.900 --> 00:04:33.700
you are a rare treasure to our guild.

00:04:33.739 --> 00:04:35.659
If you are willing,

00:04:35.940 --> 00:04:37.379
choose an auspicious day,

00:04:37.380 --> 00:04:39.220
put on this mask,

00:04:39.380 --> 00:04:42.457
and we shall stand together
through life and death.

00:04:57.260 --> 00:04:58.539
What are you doing?

00:05:05.940 --> 00:05:07.220
Your Highness.

00:05:09.659 --> 00:05:10.539
Wei Cheng.

00:05:10.620 --> 00:05:11.659
Where is Gu Chengye?

00:05:12.260 --> 00:05:13.778
Official Gu says
the case has progressed.

00:05:13.779 --> 00:05:15.449
He is waiting
for you in the ginkgo grove.

00:05:15.450 --> 00:05:16.461
The carriage is ready,

00:05:16.462 --> 00:05:17.862
and waiting outside.

00:05:18.700 --> 00:05:20.820
Why did he not come himself?

00:05:20.859 --> 00:05:22.299
Is it urgent?

00:05:24.260 --> 00:05:27.920
Yes. He left in haste.

00:05:28.099 --> 00:05:29.499
What happened?

00:05:29.659 --> 00:05:31.539
Wei Cheng, do not conceal it.

00:05:33.779 --> 00:05:35.059
Official Gu...

00:05:35.659 --> 00:05:37.179
He forbade me to speak.

00:05:37.580 --> 00:05:38.738
But he discovered

00:05:38.739 --> 00:05:40.019
that the hidden leader

00:05:40.020 --> 00:05:42.380
behind the Shengtang Guild
is Dowager Consort.

00:05:42.580 --> 00:05:44.399
He intends to report this
before the Emperor

00:05:44.400 --> 00:05:45.600
and reveal the truth.

00:05:46.099 --> 00:05:47.900
Yet he knows well

00:05:48.179 --> 00:05:49.460
that once he goes,

00:05:49.739 --> 00:05:51.260
it will be taken as defiance,

00:05:51.580 --> 00:05:53.619
and he is unlikely to recover from it.

00:05:54.859 --> 00:05:56.059
So he...

00:05:57.260 --> 00:05:58.140
He...

00:05:58.339 --> 00:05:59.900
He arranged for you to leave.

00:06:04.987 --> 00:06:08.095
(Lasting peace)

00:06:10.739 --> 00:06:11.820
(Gu Chengye,)

00:06:12.460 --> 00:06:14.780
(I will not let you face this alone.)

00:06:15.179 --> 00:06:16.345
(No matter what happens,)

00:06:16.900 --> 00:06:18.580
(I will stand behind you.)

00:06:20.779 --> 00:06:21.979
How dare you.

00:06:22.125 --> 00:06:23.145
Gu Chengye,

00:06:23.460 --> 00:06:25.307
do you know whom you accuse?

00:06:25.859 --> 00:06:27.220
She is my adoptive mother.

00:06:28.060 --> 00:06:29.820
Without solid proof,

00:06:29.979 --> 00:06:31.739
are you asking me

00:06:31.859 --> 00:06:33.738
to bear the charge of unfilial cruelty?

00:06:33.739 --> 00:06:35.220
A ruler is father to his people.

00:06:35.539 --> 00:06:37.859
Your Majesty is father to the realm.

00:06:37.979 --> 00:06:39.299
I beg Your Majesty

00:06:39.620 --> 00:06:40.778
to judge impartially,

00:06:40.779 --> 00:06:41.900
to investigate thoroughly,

00:06:42.339 --> 00:06:45.059
and restore clarity
and justice to the world.

00:06:45.060 --> 00:06:46.419
Insolence.

00:06:47.900 --> 00:06:49.580
Do you know this jade ruyi

00:06:49.820 --> 00:06:51.178
was crafted by the late Emperor?

00:06:51.179 --> 00:06:52.820
There is but one pair.

00:06:53.020 --> 00:06:54.460
One remains with me.

00:06:55.339 --> 00:06:56.739
The one you present

00:06:58.260 --> 00:06:59.499
is a forgery.

00:06:59.979 --> 00:07:01.298
You bring false evidence

00:07:01.299 --> 00:07:03.260
to accuse the Imperial Dowager Consort.

00:07:03.940 --> 00:07:05.900
How am I to judge fairly?

00:07:07.437 --> 00:07:08.637
Guards.

00:07:09.020 --> 00:07:11.380
Take Gu Chengye to the Imperial Prison.

00:07:17.500 --> 00:07:19.659
Aunt, your foresight was flawless.

00:07:19.700 --> 00:07:21.778
Gu Chengye did uncover

00:07:21.779 --> 00:07:23.419
the secret within the Beauty Portrait.

00:07:23.580 --> 00:07:24.738
We let him

00:07:24.739 --> 00:07:27.460
present a false jade ruyi
before the throne.

00:07:27.500 --> 00:07:30.099
Now he has been confined
by imperial decree.

00:07:33.099 --> 00:07:34.340
However,

00:07:34.620 --> 00:07:36.539
after all these years,

00:07:36.837 --> 00:07:39.580
has the real jade ruyi
still not been found?

00:07:40.580 --> 00:07:42.700
All who went there that day

00:07:43.140 --> 00:07:44.924
have been silenced.

00:07:44.925 --> 00:07:47.005
All but Zhou Zihua.

00:07:48.179 --> 00:07:49.979
I have watched him for years.

00:07:50.179 --> 00:07:52.700
He likely does not know
where the jade ruyi is.

00:07:54.339 --> 00:07:56.778
In any case, we must proceed carefully.

00:07:56.779 --> 00:07:59.045
No loose ends.

00:08:00.739 --> 00:08:01.900
Understood.

00:08:11.580 --> 00:08:13.020
Mother,

00:08:13.979 --> 00:08:16.299
you have plotted for so many years,

00:08:16.500 --> 00:08:18.124
like dark clouds blotting out the sun.

00:08:18.125 --> 00:08:19.900
Yet today,

00:08:20.219 --> 00:08:22.659
someone dares to uncover the truth.

00:08:24.900 --> 00:08:26.299
These clouds

00:08:26.300 --> 00:08:28.220
should clear at last.

00:08:33.939 --> 00:08:35.019
(Gu Chengye,)

00:08:35.539 --> 00:08:38.457
(the Shengtang Guild has drawn
most court officials to its side,)

00:08:38.579 --> 00:08:40.060
(and harbors rebellious intent.)

00:08:41.179 --> 00:08:43.099
(I am beset on all sides.)

00:08:43.500 --> 00:08:45.739
(You are the only one I can trust.)

00:08:46.340 --> 00:08:49.700
(I need you to stage this with me,)

00:08:50.059 --> 00:08:51.859
(to draw out the one behind it all.)

00:08:51.860 --> 00:08:54.095
(The Court of Judicial Review)

00:08:54.740 --> 00:08:55.778
Miss Song,

00:08:55.779 --> 00:08:57.178
you are but a commoner.

00:08:57.179 --> 00:08:59.139
This is no place for you.

00:09:01.380 --> 00:09:03.300
Gu Chengye, you fool.

00:09:21.287 --> 00:09:25.299
♪Even if I drift
within a darkened whirl♪

00:09:25.300 --> 00:09:27.938
♪Kindred souls
meet the light and become one♪

00:09:27.939 --> 00:09:29.060
(Gu Chengye,)

00:09:29.299 --> 00:09:31.180
(I will get you out.)

00:09:31.500 --> 00:09:34.099
Miss Song, what should we do?

00:09:34.380 --> 00:09:36.379
(How could it be forged evidence?)

00:09:36.900 --> 00:09:38.700
(Where is the real proof?)

00:09:40.459 --> 00:09:41.779
(I have it.)

00:09:43.475 --> 00:09:44.596
Wei Cheng,

00:09:44.900 --> 00:09:46.220
I need your help.

00:09:46.539 --> 00:09:48.700
I cannot watch him fall alone.

00:09:48.740 --> 00:09:50.180
I must save him.

00:09:50.612 --> 00:09:51.530
He said

00:09:51.531 --> 00:09:53.572
there may be a lead with someone.

00:09:54.140 --> 00:09:55.782
That person is Zhou Zihua.